{
  "title": "FontFactory",
  "description": "AssetFactory implementation that loads web-font binary data (WOFF, WOFF2, TTF, OTF) and produces a parsed FontFace. By default each created font is registered with `document.fonts`, making it globally available to CSS and Canvas without any further steps. Fonts added this way are automatically removed from `document.fonts` when FontFactory.destroy is called.",
